text: Yahudi bhandachanh ujaira allahako chora hun. Ra isa'i bhandachanh masiha allahako chora hun. Yo vacana uniharuko aphnai mukhako kura ho. Yiniharule ti manisaharuko kura garirakheka chan jasale yasabhanda aghi inkara garisakeka chan. Allahale yiniharula'i khatama parnecha! Atah yiniharu kata lagdaichan
